OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues temporary
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,FThe equalities watchdog has issued
OL,7,Ftemporary guidance on single-sex
OL,8,Fspaces after the Supreme Court ruled
OL,9,Fthat the term woman is defined by
OL,10,Fbiological sex.
OL,12,FTrans women "should not be permitted
OL,13,Fto use the women's facilities" in
OL,14,Fworkplaces or public-facing services
OL,15,Flike shops and hospitals, the Equality
OL,16,Fand Human Rights Commission (EHRC)
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FThe same rule applies to trans men,
OL,20,Fwho are biologically female, using
OL,21,Fmen's toilets.
