OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues temporary
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,FThe guidance has been released as
OL,7,F"many people have questions about the
OL,8,Fjudgment and what it means for them",
OL,9,Fthe EHRC said.
OL,11,FSchools must provide single-sex
OL,12,Fchanging facilities to boys and girls
OL,13,Fover the age of eight, according to
OL,14,Fthe new guidance.
