OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues temporary
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,FThe watchdog said "suitable
OL,7,Falternative provisions may be
OL,8,Frequired" for trans pupils, as trans
OL,9,Fgirls "should not be permitted to use
OL,10,Fthe girls' toilet or changing
OL,11,Ffacilities, and pupils who identify as
OL,12,Ftrans boys (biological girls) should
OL,13,Fnot be allowed to use the boys' toilet
OL,14,For changing facilities".
OL,16,FThe watchdog also stated that sports
OL,17,Fclubs and other associations with 25
OL,18,For more members are allowed to be
OL,19,Fexclusively for biological men or
OL,20,Fwomen.
