OL,3,CEqualities watchdog issues temporary
OL,4,Cguidance on single-sex spaces
OL,6,FSuch clubs "can be limited to people
OL,7,Fwho each have two protected
OL,8,Fcharacteristics", the guidance said.
OL,10,FThis would mean, for example, that a
OL,11,Flesbian women's sports club should not
OL,12,Fadmit trans women.
OL,14,FThe watchdog is working on a detailed
OL,15,Fcode of practice following the Supreme
OL,16,FCourt ruling, which it aims to submit
OL,17,Fto the Government for ministerial
OL,18,Fapproval by June.
